title: Abu Bin Yahya, Rouse Hill, Sydney, Australia.
text:
The item arrived in Sydney Australia in 3 days. Item was well packed in pristine factory condition made in Milano, Italy.
The customer service was excellent in telling the progress of my order prior to the delivery. The item was tracked via Fedex once it left Sandigliano, Italy.
I will vote 5 Stars for service and price which was a lot cheaper than any other on line outlets.
Thank you so much OTTICANET. You are the best Nicola Piccolo and the rest of the team member.
